Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why do we smoke?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ylyg7
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 8 Oct 2012
In this week's programme Mike Williams looks at why people start smoking. Nearly 50 years after the world first learned that smoking kills, millions are still picking up the habit. He also discovers who was behind one of the most lethal inventions of all time - the cigarette. (Image: The silhouette of a woman as she smokes. Credit: Danny Lawson/PA Wire) Show less